Oh sorry I assumed `o' is short for `out' and `v' for `value', which 
seems not the case.

By the way, in your solution  `fst' and `snd' should be exchanged, i.e.

let a = List.map snd (List.filter (fun x -> fst x) [(out, o); (value, v)])


